<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/conversations/{id}</code></h3>
<p>Returns the specified message if it has access to it</p>
<h4>URL parameters</h4>
<ul>
	<li><strong>token</strong>: </li>
</ul>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/conversations/</code></h3>
<p>Returns an array with all the messages from a conversation this user has access to</p>

<h3><strong>POST</strong> <code>/api/conversations/</code></h3>
<p>Sends a new message</p>
<h4>Request body</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>recipient</strong>: ID of the other user who'll be a member of this conversation</li>
</ul>
